item.description:
&ldquo;dwm is an extremely fast, small, and dynamic window manager for X.&rdquo; - suckless.org
This post talks about my dwm configuration and the changes I have made to it.
Patches alwayscenter: &ldquo;All floating windows are centered, like the center patch, but without a rule.&rdquo;
attachbottom: &ldquo;New clients attach at the bottom of the stack instead of the top.&rdquo;
center first window: Adds rule to center window if it is the only client in a tag.
